X. Fame, A Lady clad in a thin and light garment, open to the middle thigh, that ſhe might run the faſter; two exceeding large wings; 
                     •••
                  ments embroider'd with eyes and ears, and blowing of a Trumpet.

VIII. 
                     Ʋrania, A beautiful Lady in an azure robe; upon her head a Coronet of bright ſtars; in her right hand the Coeleſtial globe, and in her left the Terreſtrial. Her name imports as much as heavenly; 
                     Ʋrania coeli motus ſerutatur & Aſtra.
